  "description": "Layer-3 routing health for an OpenStack deployment: router inventory, L3 agent coverage and balance, ports per network, and security-group footprint. Leads with router count and L3-agent coverage so you can see at a glance whether every router is actually scheduled to an agent that can route its traffic.",
